  "time_ut": 1661697103,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b85\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf\u0baa\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0ba4\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Import of essential goods will be banned",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Essential Commodities Importers Association informed that the import of essential commodities will be disrupted during the festive season.",
        "The association also pointed out that this situation will occur if the opportunity to import essential goods under the open account system is not available from next month.",
        "The association noted that the price of commodities in the market has decreased slightly in the last two months due to the granting of this permission.",
        "It is reported that the open account system has been implemented for two months only and will expire from next month.",
        "Therefore, the association noted that there will be a problem if the open account system is not sustained and then banks do not have enough foreign exchange to import."
      ],
